{
  "texts": [
    "This captures context based data leakages where words leak data depending on the context in which they are used.",
    "Chen et al. (2023) performs word based replacement of the queries and then rectifies the replaced words in the response.",
    "Most recently, Shen et al. (2024) propose ProSan which targets individual words using the context from the entire prompt.",
    "Our work, in contrast, does a semantic rephrasing of the entire query instead of targeting individual words.",
    "We formulate the problem of preventing input data leakage from queries to an external LLM in the form of the following two tasks:"
  ]
}